# STAGEWELL-GROUP-CHALLENGE

## Prerequisites for setup:

Download the following dependencies on your machine:

-  Node
-  Typescript

## Environment

-  The Backend will be executed using npm commands configured in the project.

## Application

The application is executed using Node's npm commands. The project uses 9 npm commands:

-  To create JavaScript files based on Typescript files

```
npm run build
```

-  Execute the simple calculator function

```
npm run simple-calculator || npm run simple-calculator:dev
```

-  Execute the prime numbers function

```
npm run prime-number || npm run prime-number:dev
```

- Execute the factorial function

```
npm run factorial || npm run factorial:dev
```

-  Execute the palindrome function

```
npm run palindrome || npm run palindrome:dev
```

-  Execute the table function

```
npm run table || npm run table:dev
```

-  Execute the count vowels function

```
npm run count-vowels || npm run count-vowels:dev
```

-  Execute the grade average function

```
npm run grade-average || npm run grade-average:dev
```

-  Execute the interest calculation function

```
npm run interest-calculation || npm run interest-calculation:dev
```

## Directory Structure

    	STAGEWELL-GROUP-CHALLENGE
    		|
                    |-- src (Source Code)
            	|       |
                    |       |-- config (Configuration files)
                    |       |-- countVowels (Vowel count rules)
                    |       |-- factorial (Factorial calculation rules)
                    |       |-- gradeAverage (Grade calculation rules)
                    |       |-- interestCalculation (Interest calculation rules)
                    |       |-- palindrome (Palindrome verification rules)
                    |       |-- primeNumbers (Prime numbers verification rules)
                    |       |-- simpleCalculator (Calculator rules)
                    |       |-- table (Multiplication table rules)
                    |       |-- utils.ts (Reusable application resources)
    		|-- .gitignore (Files ignored in version control)
    		|-- package.json
    		|-- tsconfig.json (TypeScript compilation settings)

## Installation

1. Download the directory to your machine

```
git clone https://github.com/carlos-504/stagewell-group-challenge.git
```

2. To install project dependencies

```
npm install
```
